    S:gt.blockmachines.componentassemblyline.tooltip_secondary=§fDimensions: §69§7x§610§7x§633§7 (§6W§7x§6H§7x§6L§7) \n§fStructure: \n   §fController: §7Front center, 8th layer\n§6   644x §r§7Advanced Iridium Plated Machine Casing\n§6   124x §r§7Advanced Filter Casing\n§6   280x §r§7Any Tiered Glass (UV+)\n§6   30x §r§7Assembler Machine Casing\n§6   43x §r§7Component Assembly Line Casing (tiered)\n§6   126x §r§7PBI Pipe Casing\n§6   4x §r§7Tungstensteel Frame Box\n§6   55x §r§7Assembly Line Casing\n§f   Input Bus: §7Start of conveyor belt\n§f   Output Bus: §7End of conveyor belt\n§f   Energy Hatch: §7Second-top layer\n§f   Maintenance Hatch: §7Around the controller\n§f   Input Hatch: §7Bottom left and right corners\n   Uses sub channel §6glass§r§7 for §6Glass Tier\n   Uses sub channel §6component_casing§r§7 for §6Component Assembly Line Casing Tier\n   §7§m------------------------------\n§fTo see the structure, use a§9 Structure§1Lib §r§fHologram Projector on the Controller!
