    S:gt.blockmachines.dissolution_tank.tooltip_secondary=§fDimensions: §65§7x§65§7x§65§7 (§6W§7x§6H§7x§6L§7) §c(Hollow)\n§fStructure: \n   §fController: §7Front center, 2nd layer\n§6   42x §r§7Clean Stainless Steel Machine Casing\n§6   24x §r§7Any Borosilicate Glass\n§6   9x §r§7Heat Proof Machine Casing\n§f   Input Hatch: §7Any Stainless Steel Casing\n§f   Input Bus: §7Any Stainless Steel Casing\n§f   Output Hatch: §7Any Stainless Steel Casing\n§f   Output Bus: §7Any Stainless Steel Casing\n§f   Maintenance Hatch: §7Any Stainless Steel Casing\n   Uses sub channel §6glass§r§7 for §6Glass Tier\n   §7§m------------------------------\n§fTo see the structure, use a§9 Structure§1Lib §r§fHologram Projector on the Controller!
    S:gt.blockmachines.dysonswarm.name=ダイソンスォーム管理ユニット
    S:gt.blockmachines.dysonswarm.tooltip=Machine Type: §eDyson Swarm§r\n§o%s\nPut Dyson Swarm Modules in the Input Bus(es) to send them to the next star.\nOutputs §a10,000,000*§9§lD§r §7EU/t per module up to §a10,000\nEach hour, §6§lI§r§a * (2 * 0.066) / (exp(-0.00005 * (§6§lI§r§a - 1)) + exp(0.00003 * §b§lC§r§a)) §7of modules are destroyed.\n§b§lC§r§bomputation/s§r, §6§lI§r§6nitial module amount, §9§lD§r§9imension-dependent factor §7(check quest for values)\nRequires §a3,600,000L/h §7of Gelid Cryotheum.\nR-Click with a Plunger to extract as many Modules to your inventory as possible.\nSneaking will dump the rest on the ground.\n§aSupports TecTech Multi-Amp and Laser Hatches!\n§7§m-----------------------------------------\nHold §l[LSHIFT]§r§7 to display structure guidelines
    S:gt.blockmachines.dysonswarm.tooltip_secondary=§fDimensions: §616§7x§620§7x§616§7 (§6W§7x§6H§7x§6L§7) \n§fStructure: \n   §fController: §7Front bottom center of the Dyson Swarm Energy Receiver Base\n§f   Dynamo Hatch: §7Can use Single- and/or Multi-Amp Dynamo Hatches and/or Laser Source Hatches (1 - 12)\n§f   Input Bus: §71 - 11\n§f   Input Hatch: §71 - 11\n§f   Optical Reception Connector: §71 - 24\n   \n   §oAdditionally needed:\n§6   53x§7 - §664x §r§7Energy Receiver Base Casing\n§6   81x §r§7Energy Receiver Dish Block\n§6   62x§7 - §672x §r§7Module Deployment Unit Base Casing\n§6   1x §r§7Module Deployment Unit Core\n§6   32x §r§7Module Deployment Unit Superconducting Magnet\n§6   115x§7 - §6138x §r§7Control Center Base Casing\n§6   20x §r§7Control Center Primary Windings\n§6   12x §r§7Control Center Secondary Windings\n§6   128x §r§7Control Center Toroid Casing\n§6   256x §r§7Ultra High Strength Concrete Floor\n§6   9x §r§7Awakened Draconium Coil Block\n§6   1x §r§7Hermetic Casing X\n§6   16x §r§7Titanium Frame Box\n§6   23x §r§7HSS-S Frame Box\n§6   64x §r§7Superconductor Base UHV Frame Box\n   §7§m------------------------------\n§fTo see the structure, use a§9 Structure§1Lib §r§fHologram Projector on the Controller!
