    S:gt.blockmachines.electricimplosioncompressor.name=電動内破圧縮機
    S:gt.blockmachines.electricimplosioncompressor.tooltip=Machine Type: §eImplosion Compressor, EIC§r\n§4DEPRECATED - Controller will be removed in next major update!\n§4Check NEI for new Controller and conversion recipe\nExplosions are fun!\nUses electricity instead of Explosives\n§6Parallels§7 are determined by §fContainment Block§7 Tier\n§fNeutronium§7 : §61§7 Parallel\n§cInfinity§7 : §64§7 Parallels\n§8Transcendent Metal§7 : §616§7 Parallels\n§dSpacetime§7 : §664§7 Parallels\n§3Universium§7 : §6256§7 Parallels\nThis machine can run recipes at most 1 tiers above its average energy hatch tier\n§aSupports TecTech Multi-Amp and Laser Hatches!\n§7§m-----------------------------------------\nHold §l[LSHIFT]§r§7 to display structure guidelines
    S:gt.blockmachines.electricimplosioncompressor.tooltip.15563=Machine Type: §eImplosion Compressor, EIC§r\nExplosions are fun!\nUses electricity instead of Explosives\n§6Parallels§7 are determined by §fContainment Block§7 Tier\n§fNeutronium§7 : §61§7 Parallel\n§cInfinity§7 : §64§7 Parallels\n§8Transcendent Metal§7 : §616§7 Parallels\n§dSpacetime§7 : §664§7 Parallels\n§3Universium§7 : §6256§7 Parallels\nEnergy Hatch Tier is limited by Glass Tier\n§c§l§nUMV§r§7-glass unlocks all above energy tiers\nThis machine can run recipes at most 1 tiers above its average energy hatch tier\n§aSupports TecTech Multi-Amp and Laser Hatches!\n§7§m-----------------------------------------\nHold §l[LSHIFT]§r§7 to display structure guidelines\nStructure by: §a§6Pix3lated§r§7
    S:gt.blockmachines.electricimplosioncompressor.tooltip_secondary=§fDimensions: §63§7x§69§7x§63§7 (§6W§7x§6H§7x§6L§7) \n§fStructure: \n   §fController: §7Front center, 3rd layer\n§6   8x §r§7Solid Steel Machine Casing (minimum)\n   Casings can be replaced with Explosion Hazard Signs\n§f   Transformer-Winding Blocks: §7Outer layer 2,3,7,8\n§f   Nickel-Zinc-Ferrite Blocks: §7Inner layer 2,3,7,8\n§f   Containment Blocks: §7Layer 4,5,6\n§f   Maintenance Hatch: §7Any Solid Steel Machine casing\n§f   Input Bus: §7Any Solid Steel Machine casing\n§f   Input Hatch: §7Any Solid Steel Machine casing\n§f   Output Bus: §7Any Solid Steel Machine casing\n§f   Energy Hatch: §7Bottom middle and/or top middle\n   Uses sub channel §6piston_block§r§7 for §6Metal Block Tier\n   §7§m------------------------------\n§fTo see the structure, use a§9 Structure§1Lib §r§fHologram Projector on the Controller!
