    S:gt.blockmachines.megablastfurnace.name=メガ・電気高炉
    S:gt.blockmachines.megablastfurnace.tooltip=Machine Type: §eBlast Furnace, MEBF, MBF§r\n§6256§7 Parallels\n§b-5%§7 EU Usage per §c900K§7 above the recipe requirement\n§7§m-----------------------------------------\nIncreases Heat by §c100K§7 for every §fVoltage§7 tier past §bMV\nEvery §c1800K§7 over the recipe requirement grants 1 §dPerfect Overclock\n§7§m-----------------------------------------\n§aSupports TecTech Multi-Amp and Laser Hatches!\n§2§nUV§7-tier §fGlass§7 required for §9Tec§1Tech§7 Laser Hatches\nEnergy Hatch limited by §fGlass§7 Tier, §c§l§nUMV§7-tier unlocks all\nThis machine can run recipes regardless of tier, if given enough energy\n§5102400 §7Pollution per second\n§7§m-----------------------------------------\nHold §l[LSHIFT]§r§7 to display structure guidelines
    S:gt.blockmachines.megablastfurnace.tooltip_secondary=§fDimensions: §615§7x§620§7x§615§7 (§6W§7x§6H§7x§6L§7) §c(Hollow)\n§fStructure: \n   §fController: §7Front center, 3rd layer\n§6   0x§7 - §6447x §r§7Heat Proof Machine Casing\n§6   864x §r§7Heating Coils (tiered)\n§6   1007x §r§7Any Tiered Glass (tiered)\n   The glass tier limits the Energy Input tier\n§f   Energy Hatch: §7Any bottom layer casing\n§f   Maintenance Hatch: §7Any bottom layer casing\n§f   Muffler Hatch: §7Top middle\n§f   Input Bus: §7Any bottom layer casing\n§f   Input Hatch: §7Any bottom layer casing\n§f   Output Bus: §7Any bottom layer casing\n§f   Output Hatch: §7Any Heat Proof Machine Casing\n   Uses sub channel §6glass§r§7 for §6Glass Tier\n   Uses sub channel §6coil§r§7 for §6Heating Coils Tier\n   §7§m------------------------------\n§fTo see the structure, use a§9 Structure§1Lib §r§fHologram Projector on the Controller!
    S:gt.blockmachines.megachemicalreactor.name=メガ・化学反応器
    S:gt.blockmachines.megachemicalreactor.tooltip=Machine Type: §eChemical Reactor, MCR§r\n§4DEPRECATED - Controller will be removed in next major update!\n§4Check NEI for new Controller and conversion recipe\n§8§o"What molecule do you want to synthesize?"§r§7\n§8§o"Or do you want to replace something in this molecule?"§r§7\n§6256§7 Parallels\n§bMachine does not lose efficiency when overclocked\n§7§m-----------------------------------------\n§aSupports TecTech Multi-Amp and Laser Hatches!\n§2§nUV§7-tier §fGlass§7 required for §9Tec§1Tech§7 Laser Hatches\nEnergy Hatch limited by §fGlass§7 Tier\nThis machine can run recipes regardless of tier, if given enough energy\n§7§m-----------------------------------------\nHold §l[LSHIFT]§r§7 to display structure guidelines
    S:gt.blockmachines.megachemicalreactor.tooltip_secondary=§fDimensions: §65§7x§65§7x§69§7 (§6W§7x§6H§7x§6L§7) \n§fStructure: \n   §fController: §7Front center\n§6   46x §r§7Chemically Inert Machine Casing (minimum)\n§6   7x §r§7Fusion Coil Block\n§6   28x §r§7PTFE Pipe Casing\n§6   64x §r§7Any Tiered Glass (tiered)\n§f   Energy Hatch: §7Hint block \n§f   Maintenance Hatch: §7Hint block \n§f   Input Hatch: §7Hint block \n§f   Input Bus: §7Hint block \n§f   Output Bus: §7Hint block \n§f   Output Hatch: §7Hint block \n   Uses sub channel §6glass§r§7 for §6Glass Tier\n   §7§m------------------------------\n§fTo see the structure, use a§9 Structure§1Lib §r§fHologram Projector on the Controller!
    S:gt.blockmachines.megadistillationtower.name=メガ・蒸留塔
    S:gt.blockmachines.megadistillationtower.tooltip=Machine Type: §eDistillery, MDT§r\n§6256§7 Parallels\n§7§m-----------------------------------------\nFluids are only put out at the correct height\nThe correct height equals the slot number in the NEI recipe\n§7§m-----------------------------------------\n§aSupports TecTech Multi-Amp and Laser Hatches!\nThis machine can run recipes regardless of tier, if given enough energy\n§7§m-----------------------------------------\nHold §l[LSHIFT]§r§7 to display structure guidelines
    S:gt.blockmachines.megadistillationtower.tooltip_secondary=§fDimensions: §615§7x§616-56§7x§615§7 (§6W§7x§6H§7x§6L§7) §c(Hollow)\n§fStructure: \n   §fController: §7Front bottom center\n§f   Clean Stainless Steel Machine Casing: §715 x h - 5 (minimum)\n§f   Energy Hatch: §7Any casing\n§f   Maintenance Hatch: §7Any casing\n§f   Input Hatch: §7Any bottom layer casing\n§f   Output Bus: §7Any bottom layer casing\n§f   Output Hatch: §72-11x Output Hatches (One per Output Layer except bottom layer)\n   An "Output Layer" consists of 5 layers!\n   Uses sub channel §6height§r§7 for §6Structure Height\n   §7§m------------------------------\n§fTo see the structure, use a§9 Structure§1Lib §r§fHologram Projector on the Controller!
    S:gt.blockmachines.megaoilcracker.name=メガ・石油接触分解装置
    S:gt.blockmachines.megaoilcracker.tooltip=Machine Type: §eCracker, MOC§r\n§8§o"Thermally cracks heavy hydrocarbons into lighter fractions"§r§7\n§6256§7 Parallels\n§b-10%§7 EU Usage per §f§fHeating Coil§7§7 Tier\nup to a maximum of §b-50%§7 EU Usage\n§7§m-----------------------------------------\nGives different benefits whether it hydro or steam-cracks:\nHydro - Consumes §320%§7 less Hydrogen and outputs §325%§7 more cracked fluid\nSteam - Outputs §350%§7 more cracked fluid\n§oIn comparison to a chemical reactor§r\n§7§m-----------------------------------------\n§aSupports TecTech Multi-Amp and Laser Hatches!\n§2§nUV§7-tier §fGlass§7 required for §9Tec§1Tech§7 Laser Hatches\nEnergy Hatch limited by §fGlass§7 Tier\nThis machine can run recipes regardless of tier, if given enough energy\n§7§m-----------------------------------------\nHold §l[LSHIFT]§r§7 to display structure guidelines
    S:gt.blockmachines.megaoilcracker.tooltip_secondary=§fDimensions: §613§7x§67§7x§69§7 (§6W§7x§6H§7x§6L§7) §c(Hollow)\n§fStructure: \n   §fController: §7Front bottom center\n§6   197x §r§7Clean Stainless Steel Machine Casing\n§6   92x §r§7Coil (tiered)\n§6   196x §r§7Any Tiered Glass (tiered)\n§f   Energy Hatch: §7Hint block\n§f   Maintenance Hatch: §7Hint block\n§f   Input Hatch: §7Hint block\n§f   Output Hatch: §7Hint block\n§f   Input Hatch: §7Steam/Hydrogen ONLY, Hint block\n§f   Input Bus: §7Optional, for programmed circuit automation. Hint block\n   Uses sub channel §6glass§r§7 for §6Glass Tier\n   Uses sub channel §6coil§r§7 for §6Heating Coils Tier\n   §7§m------------------------------\n§fTo see the structure, use a§9 Structure§1Lib §r§fHologram Projector on the Controller!
    S:gt.blockmachines.megavacuumfreezer.name=メガ・真空冷却機
    S:gt.blockmachines.megavacuumfreezer.tooltip=Machine Type: §eVacuum Freezer, MVF§r\n§8§o"Handles all things cooling!"§r§7\n§6256§7 Parallels\n§7§m-----------------------------------------\n§aSupports TecTech Multi-Amp and Laser Hatches!\nThis machine can run recipes regardless of tier, if given enough energy\n§7§m-----------------------------------------\nUpgrade to Tier 2 to unlock §3Subspace Cooling.\nWill gain §6perfect overclocks §7by §aconsuming §dcoolants:\n§a75 L/s§7 : §61 §7: §dMolten Spacetime\n§a50 L/s§7 : §62 §7: §dSpatially Enlarged Fluid\n§a25 L/s§7 : §63 §7: §dMolten Eternity\n§7§m-----------------------------------------\n§3Reinforcing the structure allows the injection of exotic coolants,\n§3enabling the capture of heat energy from miniature tears in spacetime,\n§3massively increasing the efficiency of the cooling process.\n§7§m-----------------------------------------\nHold §l[LSHIFT]§r§7 to display structure guidelines
    S:gt.blockmachines.megavacuumfreezer.tooltip_secondary=§fDimensions: §615§7x§615§7x§615§7 (§6W§7x§6H§7x§6L§7) §c(Hollow)\n§fStructure: \n   §fController: §7Front center\n§f   Energy Hatch: §7Any Frost Proof Machine Casing\n§f   Maintenance Hatch: §7Any Frost Proof Machine Casing\n§f   Input Hatch: §7Any Frost Proof Machine Casing\n§f   Output Hatch: §7Any Frost Proof Machine Casing\n§f   Input Bus: §7Any Frost Proof Machine Casing\n§f   Output Bus: §7Any Frost Proof Machine Casing\n   §9Base Multi (Tier §51§9):\n§6   800x §r§7Frost Proof Machine Casing (minimum)\n   §9Tier §52§9 (Upgrades from Tier §51§9):\n§6   700x §r§7Frost Proof Machine Casing (minimum)\n§6   384x §r§7Infinity Cooled Casing\n   §7§m------------------------------\n§fTo see the structure, use a§9 Structure§1Lib §r§fHologram Projector on the Controller!
