    S:gt.blockmachines.multimachine.basiccompressor.tooltip_secondary=§fDimensions: §67§7x§68§7x§67§7 (§6W§7x§6H§7x§6L§7) §c(Hollow)\n§fStructure: \n   §fController: §7Front bottom center\n§6   95x §r§7Electric Compressor Casing (minimum)\n§6   45x §r§7Compressor Pipe Casing (minimum)\n§6   6x §r§7Any Tiered Glass\n§f   Input Bus: §7Pipe Casings on Side\n§f   Input Hatch: §7Pipe Casings on Side\n§f   Output Bus: §7Pipe Casings on Side\n§f   Energy Hatch: §7Any Electric Compressor Casing\n§f   Maintenance Hatch: §7Any Electric Compressor Casing\n   Uses sub channel §6glass§r§7 for §6Glass Tier\n   §7§m------------------------------\n§fTo see the structure, use a§9 Structure§1Lib §r§fHologram Projector on the Controller!
    S:gt.blockmachines.multimachine.beam-crafter.name=Beam Crafter
    S:gt.blockmachines.multimachine.beam-crafter.tooltip=Machine Type: §eBeam Crafter, Beam Assembler§r\nCollides two beams of particles into target materials to modify\ntheir subatomic structure\n§7§m-----------------------------------------\nInput Beams can be supplied to either Beamline Input Hatch\nInputs are consumed immediately and will wait for particles\n§7§m-----------------------------------------\nUp to §b2000000000§7 particles of each type can be buffered\nRecipe progress is determined purely by particles consumed\nfrom the buffer\n§7§m-----------------------------------------\nHas §61024§7 parallels\n§7§m-----------------------------------------\n§aSupports TecTech Multi-Amp and Laser Hatches!\n§7§m-----------------------------------------\nHold §l[LSHIFT]§r§7 to display structure guidelines\nAdded by: §aAuthor: §6Ham§fCorp§r§7
