    S:gt.blockmachines.multimachine.engraver.name=高信号域レーザー刻印装置
    S:gt.blockmachines.multimachine.engraver.tooltip=Machine Type: §eLaser Engraver, HILE§r\n§a350%§7 Speed\n§b80%§7 EU Usage\nLaser source hatch determines maximum recipe tier and parallels\nRecipe tier and overclocks limited to laser source tier + 1\nWhen using a UEV+ laser source, one multi-amp energy hatch is allowed instead of regular energy hatches\nParallels equal to the cube root of laser source amperage input\nGlass tier determines maximum laser source tier\n§c§l§nUMV§7-tier glass accepts all laser source hatches\nUse screwdriver to disable laser rendering\nUse wire cutter to toggle realism mode if you hate angled lasers\n§7§m-----------------------------------------\nHold §l[LSHIFT]§r§7 to display structure guidelines
    S:gt.blockmachines.multimachine.engraver.tooltip_secondary=§fDimensions: §65§7x§65§7x§65§7 (§6W§7x§6H§7x§6L§7) \n§fStructure: \n   §fController: §7Front bottom center\n§6   35x §r§7Laser Containment Casing (minimum)\n§6   9x §r§7Tungstensteel Frame Box\n§6   3x §r§7Any Tiered Glass (tiered)\n§f   Laser Resistant Plate: §7x1\n§f   Laser Source Hatch: §7x1\n§f   Input Bus: §7Any Casing\n§f   Input Hatch: §7Any Casing\n§f   Output Bus: §7Any Casing\n§f   Output Hatch: §7Any Casing\n§f   Energy Hatch: §7Any Casing\n§f   Maintenance Hatch: §7Any Casing\n   Uses sub channel §6glass§r§7 for §6Glass Tier\n   §7§m------------------------------\n§fTo see the structure, use a§9 Structure§1Lib §r§fHologram Projector on the Controller!
    S:gt.blockmachines.multimachine.entitycrusher.name=究極型エンティティ処理装置
    S:gt.blockmachines.multimachine.entitycrusher.tooltip=Machine Type: §ePowered Spawner, EEC§r\nSpawns and kills monsters for you!\nProduces §a120 Liquid XP§7 per operation\nPowered Spawner goes in Controller Slot\nBase energy usage: §b1920§7 EU/t\nSupports §dperfect OC!\n§7§m-----------------------------------------\nHas a minimum recipe time of 20 ticks, further overclocks multiply outputs by 4x\nRecipe time is based on mob health\nYou can additionally put a weapon inside the GUI\nIt will speed up the process and apply the looting level from the weapon (maximum 4 levels)\nEnable Weapon Preservation to prevent the weapon from breaking on it's last hit\nEnable Weapon Cycling to pull a weapon from input when the current one breaks or is moved to an output\n§cEnchanting the spikes inside the structure does nothing!\n§7§m-----------------------------------------\nIf the mob spawns §cinfernal§7, it will drain 8 times more power!\nYou can prevent §cinfernal§7 spawns by shift clicking with a screwdriver\nMobs who are always §cinfernal§7 will ignore this factor\n§7§m-----------------------------------------\nYou can enable ritual mode with a screwdriver\nWhen in ritual mode, can link to above Well of Suffering rituals\nThe Ritual must be built directly centered above the machine\nWhen linked, mobs will start to buffer and die very slowly, providing blood to the linked altar\n§7§m-----------------------------------------\nYou can disable mob animation with a soldering iron\nYou can enable batch mode with wire cutters. Providing §9 16x Time, Output, Weapon Damage\nEnergy Hatch limited by §fGlass§7 Tier, §2§nUV§7-tier unlocks all\n§7§m-----------------------------------------\nHold §l[LSHIFT]§r§7 to display structure guidelines\nAdded by: §a§4§lk§c§lu§6§lb§e§la§2§l6§a§l0§b§l0§3§l0§r§7
    S:gt.blockmachines.multimachine.entitycrusher.tooltip_secondary=§fDimensions: §65§7x§67§7x§65§7 (§6W§7x§6H§7x§6L§7) §c(Hollow)\n§fStructure: \n   §fController: §7Front bottom center\n§6   35x §r§7Solid Steel Machine Casing (minimum)\n§6   60x §r§7Any Tiered Glass\n§6   20x §r§7Steel Frame Box\n§6   9x §r§7Diamond Spike\n§f   Output Bus: §7Any bottom casing\n§f   Output Hatch: §7Any bottom casing\n§f   Energy Hatch: §7Any bottom casing\n§f   Maintenance Hatch: §7Any bottom casing\n   Uses sub channel §6glass§r§7 for §6Glass Tier\n   §7§m------------------------------\n§fTo see the structure, use a§9 Structure§1Lib §r§fHologram Projector on the Controller!
    S:gt.blockmachines.multimachine.entropic-processor.name=Entropic Processor
    S:gt.blockmachines.multimachine.entropic-processor.tooltip=Machine Type: §eEntropic Processor§r\nProcesses substances by increasing or decreasing their entropy\n§7§m-----------------------------------------\nHas §68§7 parallels by default\nUsing Advanced Alchemical Constructs increases the machine's parallels to §632§7\n§7§m-----------------------------------------\nMixes fluids or solids with a magical catalyst\nCatalyst is consumed by the recipe, then returned upon completion\n§7§m-----------------------------------------\nPerforms one perfect overclock per casing tier (Thaumium = 1 perfect OC)\n§7§m-----------------------------------------\nHold §l[LSHIFT]§r§7 to display structure guidelines
    S:gt.blockmachines.multimachine.entropic-processor.tooltip_secondary=§fDimensions: §67§7x§65§7x§67§7 (§6W§7x§6H§7x§6L§7) §c(Hollow)\n§fStructure: \n   §fController: §7Front center\n§6   24x §r§7Warded Glass\n§6   65x§7 - §697x §r§7Alchemically Resistant/Inert/Immune Casing (tiered)\n§6   3x §r§7Alchemical Construct (tiered)\n§f   Maintenance Hatch: §7Any Alchemically Resistant/Inert/Immune Casing (Hint: 1)\n§f   Input Hatch: §7Any Alchemically Resistant/Inert/Immune Casing (Hint: 1)\n§f   Input Bus: §7Any Alchemically Resistant/Inert/Immune Casing (Hint: 1)\n§f   Output Hatch: §7Any Alchemically Resistant/Inert/Immune Casing (Hint: 1)\n§f   Output Bus: §7Any Alchemically Resistant/Inert/Immune Casing (Hint: 1)\n§f   Energy Hatch: §7Any Alchemically Resistant/Inert/Immune Casing (Hint: 1)\n   Uses sub channel §6casing§r§7 for §6Alchemical Casing Tier\n   Uses sub channel §6construct§r§7 for §6Alchemical Construct Tier\n   §7§m------------------------------\n§fTo see the structure, use a§9 Structure§1Lib §r§fHologram Projector on the Controller!
    S:gt.blockmachines.multimachine.exofoundry.name=Exo-Foundry
    S:gt.blockmachines.multimachine.exofoundry.tooltip=Machine Type: §eFluid Solidifier, Foundry§r\n§616§7 Parallels per §fVoltage§7 Tier\n§a150%§7 Speed\n§8100%§7 EU Usage\nWill §lnot§7 perform §doverclocks§7 over the hatch tier without modules\nWill §lnot§7 process §1§nUIV+§7 voltage tier recipes without modules\nHas §63 Tiers§7, depending on Central Chassis Casing\nHas §62/3/4§7 Module Slots, based on machine tier\nEach Module Slot has §67§7 different options\n§6Modules§7 are selected inside the Controller\n§6Module§7 stats are shown in NEI and the Controller\nToggle Render with Screwdriver\n§aSupports TecTech Multi-Amp and Laser Hatches!\n§7§m-----------------------------------------\n§cGlorious Evolution!\n§7§m-----------------------------------------\nHold §l[LSHIFT]§r§7 to display structure guidelines
    S:gt.blockmachines.multimachine.exofoundry.tooltip_secondary=§fDimensions: §615§7x§655§7x§615§7 (§6W§7x§6H§7x§6L§7) §c(Hollow)\n§fStructure: \n   §fController: §7Front center, 2nd layer\n§6   462x §r§7Primary Exo-Foundry Casing (minimum)\n§6   548x §r§7Exo-Foundry Containment Glass\n§6   281x §r§7Inner Foundry Siphon Casing\n§6   260x §r§7Central Magnetic Chassis (tiered)\n§6   224x §r§7Netherite Frame Box\n§6   196x §r§7Central Exo-Foundry Regulation Casing\n§6   173x §r§7Black Plutonium Item Pipe Casing\n§f   Input Bus: §7Any Foundry Casing\n§f   Output Bus: §7Any Foundry Casing\n§f   Input Hatch: §7Any Foundry Casing\n§f   Energy Hatch: §7Any Foundry Casing\n   Uses sub channel §6chassis§r§7 for §6Magnetic Chassis Tier\n   §7§m------------------------------\n   Check NEI for Module structure costs\n   §7§m------------------------------\n§fTo see the structure, use a§9 Structure§1Lib §r§fHologram Projector on the Controller!
