    S:gt.blockmachines.multimachine.extractor.tooltip_secondary=§fDimensions: §65§7x§65§7x§65§7 (§6W§7x§6H§7x§6L§7) \n§fStructure: \n   §fController: §7Front bottom center\n§6   45x §r§7Stainless Steel Machine Casing (minimum)\n§6   19x §r§7Item Pipe Casing (tiered)\n§6   8x §r§7Any Tiered Glass\n§f   Input Bus: §7Any Stainless Steel Casing\n§f   Output Bus: §7Any Stainless Steel Casing\n§f   Energy Hatch: §7Any Stainless Steel Casing\n§f   Maintenance Hatch: §7Any Stainless Steel Casing\n   Uses sub channel §6glass§r§7 for §6Glass Tier\n   Uses sub channel §6item_pipe§r§7 for §6Item Pipe Casing Tier\n   §7§m------------------------------\n§fTo see the structure, use a§9 Structure§1Lib §r§fHologram Projector on the Controller!
    S:gt.blockmachines.multimachine.extremeapiary.name=産業用環境順応養蜂型大型蜜蜂飼育装置
    S:gt.blockmachines.multimachine.extremeapiary.tooltip=Machine Type: §eMega Apiary, Mapiary§r\nThe ideal home for your bees\nUse screwdriver to change primary mode (INPUT/OUTPUT/OPERATING)\nUse screwdriver + shift to change operation mode (NORMAL/SWARMER)\n§7§m-----------------------------------------\n§6Input Mode:\n- Does not take power\n- Put your queens in the input bus to put them in the internal buffer\n§7§m-----------------------------------------\n§6Output Mode:\n- Does not take power\n- Will give your bees back to output bus\n§7§m-----------------------------------------\n§6Operating Mode:\n- NORMAL:\n  - Processing time: 5 seconds\n  - Uses 1 §dLuV§7 amp per queen\n  - All bees are accelerated 64 times\n  - 8 production upgrades are applied\n  - Genetic Stabilizer upgrade applied\n  - Simulates perfect environment for your bees\n  - Additionally you can provide royal jelly to increase the outputs:\n    - 1 royal jelly grants 5% bonus per bee\n    - They will be consumed on each start of operation\n    - and be applied to that operation only\n    - Max bonus: 200%\n- SWARMER:\n  - You can only insert 1 queen\n  - It will slowly produce ignoble princesses\n  - Consumes 100 royal jelly per operation\n  - Base processing time: 1 minute\n  - Uses 1 amp §9IV§7\n  - Can overclock\n§7§m-----------------------------------------\nHold §l[LSHIFT]§r§7 to display structure guidelines\nAdded by: §a§4§lk§c§lu§6§lb§e§la§2§l6§a§l0§b§l0§3§l0§r§7 & §aRunakai§r§7
    S:gt.blockmachines.multimachine.extremeapiary.tooltip_secondary=§fDimensions: §615§7x§617§7x§615§7 (§6W§7x§6H§7x§6L§7) \n§fStructure: \n   §fController: §7Front center\n§6   190x §r§7Bronze Plated Bricks (minimum)\n§6   121x §r§7Any Tiered Glass\n   The glass tier limits the Energy Input tier\n   Regular water and IC2 Distilled Water are accepted\n§f   Flowers: §7On dirt/grass\n§f   Input Bus: §7Any casing\n§f   Output Bus: §7Any casing\n§f   Energy Hatch: §7Any casing\n§f   Maintenance Hatch: §7Any casing\n   §7§m------------------------------\n§fTo see the structure, use a§9 Structure§1Lib §r§fHologram Projector on the Controller!
    S:gt.blockmachines.multimachine.extremedieselengine.name=発展型内燃エンジン
    S:gt.blockmachines.multimachine.extremedieselengine.tooltip=Machine Type: §eCombustion Generator, ECE§r\n§4DEPRECATED - Controller will be removed in next major update!\n§4Check NEI for new Controller and conversion recipe\nSupply high rating fuel and 8000L of Lubricant per hour to run\nSupply 40L/s of Liquid Oxygen to boost output (optional)\nDefault: Produces 10900EU/t at 100% fuel efficiency\nBoosted: Produces 32700EU/t at 150% fuel efficiency\nYou need to wait for it to reach 300% to output full power\n§53840 §7Pollution per second\n§7§m-----------------------------------------\nHold §l[LSHIFT]§r§7 to display structure guidelines
    S:gt.blockmachines.multimachine.extremedieselengine.tooltip.15534=Machine Type: §eCombustion Generator, ECE§r\nSupply High Rating Fuels and §f8,000L§7 of Lubricant per hour to run\nSupply §f40L/s§7 of Liquid Oxygen to boost output (optional)\nDefault: Produces §e10,900§f EU/t§7 at §8100%§7 fuel efficiency\nBoosted: Produces §e32,700§f EU/t§7 at §b150%§7 fuel efficiency\nYou need to wait for it to reach §b300%§7 to output full power\nEngine Intake Casings must not be obstructed on top (only air blocks)\n§53840 §7Pollution per second\n§7§m-----------------------------------------\nHold §l[LSHIFT]§r§7 to display structure guidelines\nStructure by: §a§6N7Paddy§r§7
    S:gt.blockmachines.multimachine.extremedieselengine.tooltip_secondary=§fDimensions: §63§7x§63§7x§64§7 (§6W§7x§6H§7x§6L§7) \n§fStructure: \n   §fController: §7Front center\n§6   16x§7 - §622x §r§7Robust Tungstensteel Machine Casing\n§f   Titanium Gear Box Machine Casing: §7Inner 2 blocks\n§f   Extreme Engine Intake Machine Casing: §78x, ring around controller\n   Extreme Engine Intake Casings must not be obstructed in front (only air blocks)\n§f   Dynamo Hatch: §7Back center\n§f   Maintenance Hatch: §7One of the casings next to a Gear Box\n§f   Muffler Hatch: §7Top middle back, above the rear Gear Box\n§f   Input Hatch: §7HOG, next to a Gear Box\n§f   Input Hatch: §7Lubricant, next to a Gear Box\n§f   Input Hatch: §7Liquid Oxygen, optional, next to a Gear Box\n   §7§m------------------------------\n§fTo see the structure, use a§9 Structure§1Lib §r§fHologram Projector on the Controller!
    S:gt.blockmachines.multimachine.extremedieselengine.tooltip_secondary.15534=§fDimensions: §610§7x§65§7x§65§7 (§6W§7x§6H§7x§6L§7) \n§fStructure: \n   §fController: §7Front left, 2nd layer\n§6   30x §r§7Robust Tungstensteel Machine Casing (minimum)\n§6   6x §r§7Steel Gear Box Casing\n§6   12x §r§7Extreme Engine Intake Casing\n§6   32x §r§7PTFE Frame Box\n§6   10x §r§7PTFE Pipe Casing\n§6   4x §r§7Tungstensteel Turbine Casing (minimum)\n§6   12x §r§7Tungstensteel Firebox Casing\n§6   30x §r§7Chemically Inert Machine Casing\n§f   Dynamo Hatch: §7Back center\n§f   Maintenance Hatch: §7Any Robust Tungstensteel Machine Casing\n§f   Muffler Hatch: §7Any Robust Tungstensteel Machine Casing\n§f   Input Hatch: §7High Rating Fuel, next to a Gear Box\n§f   Input Hatch: §7Lubricant, next to a Gear Box\n§f   Input Hatch: §7Liquid Oxygen, optional, next to a Gear Box\n   §7§m------------------------------\n§fTo see the structure, use a§9 Structure§1Lib §r§fHologram Projector on the Controller!
    S:gt.blockmachines.multimachine.extremegreenhouse.name=究極型産業用温室
    S:gt.blockmachines.multimachine.extremegreenhouse.tooltip=Machine Type: §eCrop Farm, EIG§r\nGrow your crops like a chad!\nUse screwdriver to enable/change/disable setup mode\nUse screwdriver while sneaking to enable/disable IC2 mode\nUse wire cutters to give incoming IC2 seeds 0 humidity\nUses 1000L of water per seed per operation\nUses 1L of Weed-EX 9000 per operation per seed if it contains more than 1000 seeds\nOtherwise, around 1% of seeds will be voided each operation\nYou can insert fertilizer each operation to get more drops (max + 400)\nEnergy Hatch limited by §fGlass§7 Tier\n§7§m-----------------------------------------\n§6Setup Mode:\nDoes not take power\nThere are two modes: input / output\nInput mode: machine will take seeds from input bus and plant them\n[IC2] You need to also input block that is required under the crop\nOutput mode: machine will take planted seeds and output them\n§7§m-----------------------------------------\n§6Normal Crops:\nMinimal voltage tier: §8EV§7\nStarting with 1 slot\nEvery tier past §8EV§7, slots are multiplied by 2\nEvery slot adds 64 seed to the total seed capacity\nBase process time: 5 sec\nProcess time is divided by number of tiers past §eHV§7 (Minimum 1 sec)\nAll crops are grown at the end of the operation\nDoes not drop seeds\nCan consume up to 2 fertilizer per seed per cycle\nBoost per fertilizer: 200%\n§7§m-----------------------------------------\n§cDEPRECATED§r\n§6IC2 Crops:\nMinimal voltage tier: §dLuV§7\nMinimal glass tier: §dLuV§7\nStarting with 4 slot\nEvery tier past §dLuV§7, slots are multiplied by 4\nEvery slot adds 1 seed to the total seed capacity\nProcess time: 5 sec\nAll crops are accelerated by x32 times\nCan consume up to 40 fertilizer per seed per cycle\nBoost per fertilizer: 10%\nWeed-EX 9000 consumption is multiplied by 5\n§7§m-----------------------------------------\nHold §l[LSHIFT]§r§7 to display structure guidelines\nAdded by: §a§4§lk§c§lu§6§lb§e§la§2§l6§a§l0§b§l0§3§l0§r§7§r§7; Structure by: §aHydroCN§r§7
    S:gt.blockmachines.multimachine.extremegreenhouse.tooltip_secondary=§fDimensions: §67§7x§67§7x§69§7 (§6W§7x§6H§7x§6L§7) \n§fStructure: \n   §fController: §7Front bottom center\n§6   70x §r§7Sterile Farm Casing (minimum)\n   Tiered glass\n   The glass tier limits the Energy Input tier\n   The dirt is from RandomThings, must be tilled\n   Regular water and IC2 Distilled Water are accepted\n   Purple lamps are from ProjectRedIllumination. They can be powered and/or inverted\n§f   Maintenance Hatch: §7Any casing\n§f   Input Bus: §7Any casing\n§f   Output Bus: §7Any casing\n§f   Input Hatch: §7Any casing\n§f   Energy Hatch: §7Any casing\n   Uses sub channel §6glass§r§7 for §6Glass Tier\n   §7§m------------------------------\n§fTo see the structure, use a§9 Structure§1Lib §r§fHologram Projector on the Controller!
    S:gt.blockmachines.multimachine.fluidextractor.name=大型液体抽出装置
    S:gt.blockmachines.multimachine.fluidextractor.tooltip=Machine Type: §eFluid Extractor, LFE§r\n§68§7 Parallels per §fSolenoid§7 Tier\n§a150%§7 Speed\n§b80%§7 EU Usage\nEvery coil tier gives a §a+§7§a10%§7 speed bonus and a §b10%§7 EU/t discount (multiplicative)\nThe EU multiplier is §o0.80 * (0.90 ^ Heating Coil Tier)§7, prior to overclocks\nThe energy hatch tier is limited by the glass tier. UEV glass unlocks all tiers\n§7§m-----------------------------------------\nHold §l[LSHIFT]§r§7 to display structure guidelines
    S:gt.blockmachines.multimachine.fluidextractor.tooltip_secondary=§fDimensions: §65§7x§69§7x§65§7 (§6W§7x§6H§7x§6L§7) \n§fStructure: \n   §fController: §7Front bottom center\n§6   41x §r§7Robust Tungstensteel Machine Casing (minimum)\n§6   36x §r§7Any Tiered Glass (tiered)\n§6   7x §r§7Solenoid Superconducting Coil (tiered)\n§6   24x §r§7Heating Coils (tiered)\n§6   24x §r§7Black Steel Frame Box\n§f   Input Bus: §7Any Robust Tungstensteel Machine Casing\n§f   Output Bus: §7Any Robust Tungstensteel Machine Casing\n§f   Output Hatch: §7Any Robust Tungstensteel Machine Casing\n§f   Energy Hatch: §7Any Robust Tungstensteel Machine Casing\n§f   Maintenance Hatch: §7Any Robust Tungstensteel Machine Casing\n   Uses sub channel §6glass§r§7 for §6Glass Tier\n   Uses sub channel §6coil§r§7 for §6Heating Coils Tier\n   Uses sub channel §6solenoid§r§7 for §6Solenoid Tier\n   §7§m------------------------------\n§fTo see the structure, use a§9 Structure§1Lib §r§fHologram Projector on the Controller!
