    S:gt.blockmachines.multimachine.fuelcellmk1.tooltip=Machine Type: §eGas Turbine, SOFC§r\nOxidizes gas fuels to generate electricity without polluting the environment\nConsumes up to 40,960EU worth of fuel with up to 100% efficiency each second\nSteam production requires the SOFC to heat up completely first\nOutputs 2048EU/t and 20000L/s Steam\nAdditionally, requires 100L/s Oxygen gas\n§7§m-----------------------------------------\nHold §l[LSHIFT]§r§7 to display structure guidelines
