    S:gt.blockmachines.multimachine.nanochipassemblycomplex.name=Nanochip Assembly Complex
    S:gt.blockmachines.multimachine.nanochipassemblycomplex.tooltip=Machine Type: §eNAC, Nanochip-Assembly-Complex§r\nUses Circuit Components (§eCCs§7) to create circuits at unimaginable speeds\nClick the Logo Icon in the GUI for more information\n§7§m-----------------------------------------\n§eCCs§7 can only exist in the perfect environment present in §fVacuum Conveyor Hatches§7\nConvert items to §eCCs§7 in the control room by placing them in a §cc§eo§al§3o§br§de§5d§7 input bus\nEvery §45§7 seconds, all items in §cc§eo§al§3o§br§de§5d§7 input buses are placed\nin Vacuum Conveyor Outputs (§eVCOs§7) of the same §cc§eo§al§bo§dr§7\nFinished circuit §eCCs§7 are converted back into circuits by routing them to a §eVCI§7 in the control room\n§eCCs§7 in a §cc§eo§al§3o§br§de§5d§7 §eVCI§7 are placed in an output bus of the same §cc§eo§al§bo§dr§7\n§7§m-----------------------------------------\n§eCCs§7 must be processed into a refined version by §f§nmodules§r§7 before they\ncan be assembled into a circuit in the §aNanochip Assembly Matrix\nAll power from the energy hatch is distributed to the modules as they need it\n§aSupports TecTech Multi-Amp and Laser Hatches!\n§7§m-----------------------------------------\n§d§oHome of the Gestalt Rapidly Evolving Genesis Optimization System (GREGOS),§7\n§d§oa pseudo-sentient program overseeing circuit production in the NAC§7\n§d§oIt seems to be eager to learn more, maybe you can become friends?§7\n§7§m-----------------------------------------\nHold §l[LSHIFT]§r§7 to display structure guidelines
    S:gt.blockmachines.multimachine.nanochipassemblycomplex.tooltip_secondary=§fDimensions: §663§7x§649§7x§663§7 (§6W§7x§6H§7x§6L§7) \n§fStructure: \n§f   NAC Module: §7Any mesh interface platform on outer ring\n§6   3956x §r§7Nanochip Reinforcement Casing\n§6   2226x §r§7Nanochip Complex Glass\n§6   1720x §r§7Nanochip Mesh Interface Casing\n§6   721x §r§7Nanochip Computational Matrix Casing\n§6   53x §r§7gt.blockframes.10.name\n§6   32x §r§7Nanochip Firewall Projection Casing\n   §fVacuum Conveyor Input:§7 Any control room mesh interface casing\n   §fVacuum Conveyor Output:§7 Any control room mesh interface casing\n§f   Input Bus: §7Any control room mesh interface casing\n§f   Output Bus: §7Any control room mesh interface casing\n§f   Energy Hatch: §7Any control room mesh interface casing\n   §7§m------------------------------\n§fTo see the structure, use a§9 Structure§1Lib §r§fHologram Projector on the Controller!
    S:gt.blockmachines.multimachine.nanochipmodule.assemblymatrix.name=Nanochip Assembly Matrix
    S:gt.blockmachines.multimachine.nanochipmodule.assemblymatrix.tooltip=Machine Type: §eAssembly Matrix, NAC Module§r\nModule of the §aNanochip Assembly Complex§7\nAssembles your Circuits §eCCs§7 with Component §eCCs§7\n§7§m-----------------------------------------\nMaximum allowed recipe tier is determined by §fComponent Assembly Line Casing§7 Tier\nOverclocks recipes (Energy Hatch Tier - Recipe Casing Tier) times\n§7§m-----------------------------------------\n§d§oAfter processing your CCs through an intricate pipeline, they are finally§7\n§d§oready to be assembled into a circuit. This circuit can be converted into a real§7\n§d§oitem in the NAC control center, or processed further into a higher tier circuit§7\n§7§m-----------------------------------------\nHold §l[LSHIFT]§r§7 to display structure guidelines
    S:gt.blockmachines.multimachine.nanochipmodule.assemblymatrix.tooltip_secondary=§fDimensions: §67§7x§67§7x§67§7 (§6W§7x§6H§7x§6L§7) \n§fStructure: \n   §fController: §7Middle of the Mesh Interface Platform\n§6   25x §r§7Nanochip Reinforcement Casing\n§6   24x §r§7Nanochip Complex Glass\n§6   20x §r§7Component Assembly Line Casing (tiered)\n§6   12x §r§7gt.blockframes.10.name\n§6   8x §r§7Nanochip Mesh Interface Casing\n§6   3x §r§7Naquadah Alloy Sheetmetal\n   §fVacuum Conveyor Input:§7 Any base casing\n   §fVacuum Conveyor Output:§7 Any base casing\n   Uses sub channel §6component_casing§r§7 for §6Component Assembly Line Casing Tier\n   §7§m------------------------------\n   §fMaterial Count§r §c§lNOT§r §fIncluding Mesh Interface Platform§r\n   §7§m------------------------------\n§fTo see the structure, use a§9 Structure§1Lib §r§fHologram Projector on the Controller!
