    S:gt.blockmachines.supercriticalsteamturbine.tooltip=Machine Type: §eSteam Turbine, LST-SC§r\nNeeds a Turbine, place inside controller\nUse Supercritical Steam to generate power\nOutputs 1L of SH Steam per 1L of SC Steam as well as producing power\nPower output depends on turbine and fitting\nUse screwdriver to adjust fitting of turbine\n§7§m-----------------------------------------\nHold §l[LSHIFT]§r§7 to display structure guidelines\nStructure by: §a§6hugetrust§r§7
