    S:gt.blockmachines.thtr.tooltip=Machine Type: §eHigh Temperature Reactor, THTR§r\nNeeds to be primed with 730,000 of helium\nNeeds a constant supply of §bcoolant§7 while running\nNeeds at least §6100K§7 Fuel pebbles to start operation (can hold up to 675k pebbles)\nConsumes up to §60.5%§7 of total Fuel Pellets per Operation depending on efficiency\nEfficiency decreases exponentially if the internal buffer is not completely filled\nReactor will take §b4800L/t§7 of coolant multiplied by efficiency\nUses 3,840 EU/t\nOne Operation takes 9 hours\n§7§m-----------------------------------------\nHold §l[LSHIFT]§r§7 to display structure guidelines
