    S:gt.blockmachines.treefarm.controller.tier.single.name=樹木成長シミュレーター
    S:gt.blockmachines.treefarm.controller.tier.single.tooltip=Machine Type: §eTree Farm, TGS§r\n§4DEPRECATED - Controller will be removed in next major update!\n§4Check NEI for new Controller and conversion recipe\nFarms and harvests trees using EU\nPlace a sapling in the controller slot\nPlace a tool in an input bus\nDifferent tools are required for different outputs\nAdvanced tools multiply output amount\n  Logs: Saw (1x), Buzzsaw (2x), Chainsaw (4x)\n  Saplings: Branch Cutter (1x), Grafter (4x)\n  Leaves: Shears (1x), Wire Cutter (2x), Electric Wire Cutter (4x)\n  Fruit: Knife (1x)\nMultiple tools can be used at the same time\n§7§m-----------------------------------------\nWork time is fixed at 5 seconds\nEnergy input tier multiplies output further\nOutput multiplier is equal to: 2*tier^2 - 2*tier + 5\n§5100 §7Pollution per second\n§7§m-----------------------------------------\nHold §l[LSHIFT]§r§7 to display structure guidelines
    S:gt.blockmachines.treefarm.controller.tier.single.tooltip.15541=Machine Type: §eTree Farm, TGS§r\nFarms and harvests trees using EU\nPlace a sapling in the controller slot\nPlace a tool in an input bus\nDifferent tools are required for different outputs\nAdvanced tools multiply output amount\n  Logs: Saw (1x), Buzzsaw (2x), Chainsaw (4x)\n  Saplings: Branch Cutter (1x), Grafter (4x)\n  Leaves: Shears (1x), Wire Cutter (2x), Electric Wire Cutter (4x)\n  Fruit: Knife (1x)\nMultiple tools can be used at the same time\n§7§m-----------------------------------------\nWork time is fixed at 5 seconds\nEnergy input tier multiplies output further\nOutput multiplier is equal to: 2*tier^2 - 2*tier + 5\n§5100 §7Pollution per second\n§7§m-----------------------------------------\nHold §l[LSHIFT]§r§7 to display structure guidelines\nStructure by: §a§6EvgenWarGold§r§7
    S:gt.blockmachines.treefarm.controller.tier.single.tooltip_secondary=§fDimensions: §63§7x§63§7x§63§7 (§6W§7x§6H§7x§6L§7) §c(Hollow)\n§fStructure: \n   §fController: §7Front center\n§6   8x §r§7Sterile Farm Casing (minimum)\n§f   Input Bus: §7Any casing\n   §eStocking Input Buses and Crafting Input Buses/Buffers are not allowed!\n§f   Output Bus: §7Any casing\n§f   Energy Hatch: §7Any casing\n§f   Maintenance Hatch: §7Any casing\n§f   Muffler Hatch: §7Any casing\n   §7§m------------------------------\n§fTo see the structure, use a§9 Structure§1Lib §r§fHologram Projector on the Controller!
    S:gt.blockmachines.treefarm.controller.tier.single.tooltip_secondary.15541=§fDimensions: §67§7x§67§7x§67§7 (§6W§7x§6H§7x§6L§7) §c(Hollow)\n§fStructure: \n   §fController: §7Front bottom center\n§6   45x §r§7Sterile Farm Casing (minimum)\n§6   60x §r§7Steel Frame Box\n§6   57x §r§7Any tiered glass\n§6   25x §r§7Dirt/Grass\n   Oak Wood and Leaves can be placed manually. If not, they will be placed automatically.\n§f   Input Bus: §7Any Sterile Farm Casing\n   §eStocking Input Buses and Crafting Input Buses/Buffers are not allowed!\n§f   Output Bus: §7Any Sterile Farm Casing\n§f   Energy Hatch: §7Any Sterile Farm Casing\n§f   Maintenance Hatch: §7Any Sterile Farm Casing\n§f   Muffler Hatch: §7Any Sterile Farm Casing\n   §7§m------------------------------\n§fTo see the structure, use a§9 Structure§1Lib §r§fHologram Projector on the Controller!
    S:gt.blockmachines.universalchemicalfuelengine.name=万能型化学燃料エンジン
    S:gt.blockmachines.universalchemicalfuelengine.tooltip=Machine Type: §eChemical Engine, UCFE§r\nBURNING BURNING BURNING\nUse combustible liquid to generate power\nYou need to supply Combustion Promoter to keep it running\nIt will consume all the fuel and combustion promoter in the hatch every second\nEnergy output to the dynamo will be distributed over the next second\nIf the Dynamo Hatch's buffer fills up, the machine will stop\nIf the amount of energy to be produced is higher than the dynamo hatch can handle then all produced energy will void\nWhen turned on, there is a 10-second period where the machine will not stop\nEven if it doesn't stop, all the fuel in the hatch will be consumed\nThe efficiency is determined by the proportion of Combustion Promoter to fuel\nThe higher the amount of promoter, the higher the efficiency\nFollows an exponential curve exp(-C/(p/x))*1.5, where x is the amount of fuel in liters, p is the amount of promoter in liters\nand C depends on the fuel type. Diesel: C=0.04; Gas: C=0.04; Rocket fuel: C=0.005\nIt creates sqrt(Current Output Power) pollution every second\nIf you forget to supply Combustion Promoter, this engine will swallow all the fuel §ewithout outputting energy\nThe efficiency is up to 150%\n§aSupports TecTech Multi-Amp and Laser Hatches!\n§7§m-----------------------------------------\nHold §l[LSHIFT]§r§7 to display structure guidelines\nStructure by: §a§6TimTems§r§7
    S:gt.blockmachines.universalchemicalfuelengine.tooltip.32001=Machine Type: §eChemical Engine, UCFE§r\n§4DEPRECATED - Controller will be removed in next major update!\n§4Check NEI for new Controller and conversion recipe\nBURNING BURNING BURNING\nUse combustible liquid to generate power\nYou need to supply Combustion Promoter to keep it running\nIt will consume all the fuel and combustion promoter in the hatch every second\nEnergy output to the dynamo will be distributed over the next second\nIf the Dynamo Hatch's buffer fills up, the machine will stop\nIf the amount of energy to be produced is higher than the dynamo hatch can handle then all produced energy will void\nWhen turned on, there is a 10-second period where the machine will not stop\nEven if it doesn't stop, all the fuel in the hatch will be consumed\nThe efficiency is determined by the proportion of Combustion Promoter to fuel\nThe higher the amount of promoter, the higher the efficiency\nFollows an exponential curve exp(-C/(p/x))*1.5, where x is the amount of fuel in liters, p is the amount of promoter in liters\nand C depends on the fuel type. Diesel: C=0.04; Gas: C=0.04; Rocket fuel: C=0.005\nIt creates sqrt(Current Output Power) pollution every second\nIf you forget to supply Combustion Promoter, this engine will swallow all the fuel §ewithout outputting energy\nThe efficiency is up to 150%\n§aSupports TecTech Multi-Amp and Laser Hatches!\n§7§m-----------------------------------------\nHold §l[LSHIFT]§r§7 to display structure guidelines
