    S:gt.blockmachines.voidminer2.tooltip=Machine Type: §eMiner, VM§r\nConsumes 131,072 EU/t\nCan be supplied with §b2 L/s§7 of Noble gases to boost §6output\n§dNeon§7 : §64x§7\n§bKrypton§7 : §68x§7\n§3Xenon§7 : §616x§7\n§9Oganesson§7 : §664x§7\nWill output 4 Ores per Second depending on the Dimension it is built in\nOres selected in the Controller UI or added to an Input Bus are\nadded to the Whitelist/Blacklist\nUse the Controller UI or a screwdriver to toggle Whitelist/Blacklist\nBlacklisted or non Whitelisted Ore will be §4VOIDED\nCan copy/paste Ore filter configuration with a §aData Stick\n§7§m-----------------------------------------\nHold §l[LSHIFT]§r§7 to display structure guidelines
